purple-signald

A libpurple/Pidgin plugin for signald (signal, formerly textsecure).

Known Issues

There have been reports of incoming offline-messages getting lost. As
far as I observed, they are not lost but delayed and delivered after a
restart of signald.  Features

    Receive messages
    Send messages
    Receive files
    Receive images
    Send images
    Receive buddy list from server

Note: When signald is being run as a system service, downloaded files
may not be accessible directly to the user. Do not forget to add
yourself to the signald group.
